<h4 id="its-the-end-of-the-fiscal-year-stacy-pays-the-interest-she-owes-on-the-loan-she-used-to-buy-the-plot-of-land">It’s the End of the Fiscal Year. Stacy Pays the Interest She Owes on the Loan She Used to Buy the Plot of Land</h4>
