<p>Stacy calls the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">depreciateFixedAsset</code> function with (<a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/scripts/deploy.ts#L137" target="_blank">code)</a>). View the <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.40.46%20AM.png" target="_blank">balance sheet</a>, <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.40.54%20AM.png" target="blank">income statement</a>, and <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.41.01%20AM.png" target="_blank">cash flow statement</a> after taking this action.</p>

<h4 id="stacy-pays-income-taxes">Stacy Pays Income Taxes</h4>
<p>Stacy calls the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">payTaxes</code> function with (<a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/scripts/deploy.ts#L141" target="_blank">code)</a>). View the <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.41.11%20AM.png" target="_blank">balance sheet</a>, <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.41.17%20AM.png" target="blank">income statement</a>, and <a href="https://github.com/saiakilesh/automated-crypto-accounting/blob/main/pics/Screen%20Shot%202022-04-13%20at%205.41.25%20AM.png" target="_blank">cash flow statement</a> after taking this action. Note the following facts:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Retained earnings on the balance sheet equals net income on the income statement.</li>
  <li>Cash on the balance sheet equals ending cash balance on the cash flow statement.</li>
</ul>

<p>This implies that our code works as desired.</p>
